<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	黄元吉道教思想略说
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<div style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%" align="center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">刘国梁</span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">黄元吉，名裳，清末江西省丰城人。著有《乐育堂语录》、《道德经精义》。其姓字与元代净明派黄元吉相同。其丹功为中黄直透。他的基本思想是</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">: </font></span></div>
<div style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一、理气合而生万物</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">黄元吉说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;夫太极，理也。阴阳，气也。理气合一，而天地人物生焉&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷三</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。他认为，&ldquo;理&rdquo;与气相结合，即生成天地万物和人。&ldquo;理&rdquo;是什么</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;理&rdquo;即是太极，即是性命，也就是性。通俗地说，理即性，乃指心中至善之理。所谓&ldquo;理气合一日仁&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《道德经精义》第五章</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">，归根结底，就是说天地万物和人是由&ldquo;仁&rdquo;派生出来的。</span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">黄元吉还说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">鸿濛未判的元气，混沌初开的始气叫做&ldquo;真一之气&rdquo;。它在先天而不见其先，居后天而不见其后，&ldquo;虽非后天之精气神，亦非先天之精气神，实为后天精气神之根本，先天精气神之主宰&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷二</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。他认为，这个&ldquo;真一之气&rdquo;是&ldquo;生天生地生人生物，莫不由之，成仙成佛，亦岂外是&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">同上</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">的。&ldquo;何谓真一之气</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《诗》日</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&lsquo;维夭之命，于穆不已是&rsquo;。妙</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《道德经精义》第十四章注</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">显然，这是把&ldquo;真一之气&rdquo;与天命等同的了。尽</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">'i;</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">黄元吉有时又把万物之源叫做&ldquo;道&rdquo;、&ldquo;太极&rdquo;、&ldquo;理&rdquo;或&ldquo;先天之气&rdquo;、&ldquo;太和之气&rdquo;。但是，他所说的万物之源确是一种精神。对于心</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">犯观</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">境</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">客观</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">的关系，黄元占也有所认识。他认为，心不与俱灭、&ldquo;知觉不起时，万境皆灭&rdquo;，&ldquo;知觉纷起时，万境皆生&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷一</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。就是说，客观外物不是独立于人们的主观意识之外的，是随人们知觉的变化而变化的。</span></div>
<div style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二、明心见性与性命双修</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">黄元吉说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;性是慈爱的物事，命是身中氛氢之元气&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷二</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。又说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;夫先天之心即性，先天之性，即虚无元气，要之一虚而已矣&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">同上卷一</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。他认为，性即是理，即是仁，即是元气，是先验性的。性和命比较，性则更为重要。二者的关系是</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;性是命之根，命是性之蒂。无命则性无所依，无性则命无主，二者是二而一也。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《论性命双修》，见《中华仙学》，台湾克善美出版社第</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">631</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">页</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;无性则命无由生，无命则性无所立&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷一</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。他把&ldquo;性&rdquo;分为气性和真性，认为气性不除，人有烦脑，真性即随之消灭。为了使真性永存人身，他主张性命双修。如何实现性命双修呢</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">关键是炼心，做到牢拴意马，紧锁心猿。步骤是</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">一</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">以性立命，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">二</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">以命了性，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">三</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">性命合一。性命双修的秘诀是</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">动处炼性，静处炼命。人能做到&ldquo;惟精帷一，允执厥中&rdquo;即养性，做到宝精裕气即立命。</span></div>
<div style="TEXT-INDENT: 26pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">对于心、性、情的关系，黄元吉提出了</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp; </font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;心载性&rdquo;、&ldquo;性统心&rdquo;的观点。他说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;心性无主，惟无心无依，心所以载性，性所以统心&rdquo;又《乐育堂语录》卷一</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。他认为，性有气性、真性，情有妄情、真情，心有真心妄心。所谓明心见性，就是做到&ldquo;推虚则灵，灵则明&rdquo;，即进入无识无知、内想不出，外想不入的境界，实现&ldquo;事来应之，事去已之，方见真心&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷二</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">，如镜之照物，无染无著，心到此地，即是明心。至于见性，他说</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">&ldquo;性即仁也，我若有觉，即是真正见性也&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《乐育堂语录》卷三</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">。就是说，只要悟得仁即是见性。其实，明心见性就是做到&ldquo;心空无物，即明心见性矣。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">《道德经精义》第</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">71</font></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">章</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></div>
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 附件 -->
	   		
		   		
			
	   </div>
   
   
